PT Clusters Used84 / 128
Macrocells Used72 / 128
Registers Used33 / 128

Notes

Virtual Address Unit for the Vera homebrew CPU. Mainly consists of a 32b (unsigned) + 16b (signed) adder, with an overflow output and some preprocessing on the 16b input to allow it to be sourced from microcode or one of 3 locations within the instruction word.
